'''透納氏症'''（{{lang-en|Turner syndrome}}，[[縮寫|縮寫]]：{{lang|en|TS}}），或稱'''{{lang|en|45,X}}'''、'''{{lang|en|45,X0}}'''，為{{le|性腺發育不良|Gonodal dysgenesis}}的一種，是[[雌性|雌性]]個體因[[X染色體|X染色體]]部分或完全缺失而引發的疾病<ref name=NIH2013Def>{{cite web|title=Turner Syndrome: Overview|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/Pages/default.aspx|publisher={{tsl|en|Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development||Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development}}|accessdate=2015-03-15|date=2013-04-03|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402112322/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/Pages/default.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。透納氏症患者的症狀各異<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Sym/> -->，患者常常會有短而成{{tsl|en|webbed neck|蹼狀的頸部}}、{{tsl|en|low-set ears|低耳位}}、頸後髮際線較低、[[矮小|矮小]]，出生時即手腳[[水腫|水腫]]等特徵<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Sym/> -->。一般來說，透納氏症患者[[閉經|沒有月經]]、[[乳房|乳房]]不發育而且[[不孕|不孕]]<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Sym/> -->，且患有[[先天性心臟病|先天性心臟病]]、[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]以及[[甲狀腺功能低下症|甲狀腺功能低下症]]的機率較正常人高<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Sym/> -->。大部分的透納氏症患者的智力水平正常<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Sym/> -->，但許多患者的{{tsl|en|spatial visualization|空間視覺能力}}低下，比如學習數學所需要的{{tsl|en|spatial visualization|空間視覺能力}}<ref name=NIH2012Sym>{{cite web|title=What are the symptoms of Turner syndrome?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/conditioninfo/pages/symptoms.aspx|publisher=Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development|accessdate=2015-03-15|date=2012-11-30|archive-date=2015-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150327033016/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/conditioninfo/pages/symptoms.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。透納氏症患者有視覺和聽覺障礙的機率也較正常人高<ref name=NEJM2004/>。

== 病因與診斷 ==
<!-- Cause and diagnosis -->
透納氏症並不是一種會[[遺傳|遺傳]]自父母親的疾病<ref name=NIH2012Epi/>。目前所知沒有任何環境因素會導致此病症，同時也和媽媽的懷孕年齡沒有關係<ref name=NIH2012Epi/><ref>{{cite book|author1=Michael Cummings|title=Human Heredity: Principles and Issues|date=2015|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=9781305480674|page=161|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Dz9-BAAAQBAJ&pg=PT161|access-date=2016-06-28|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001134040/https://books.google.com/books?id=Dz9-BAAAQBAJ&pg=PT161|dead-url=no}}</ref>。透納氏症主要肇因於[[染色體異常|染色體異常]]，為X染色體部份或整條有缺失<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Con/> -->或改變而致。大部分人擁有46條染色體，但患有透納氏症的患者卻僅有45條<ref name=NIH2012Con>{{cite web|title=Turner Syndrome: Condition Information|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|publisher=Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development|accessdate=2015-03-15|date=2012-11-30|archive-date=2015-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150329012532/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在某些情況下，染色體的異常現象只出現在部分細胞，而其餘則沒有，這就是透納氏症的[[鑲嵌現象|鑲嵌現象]]<ref name=NEJM2004/>。在這樣的前提下，由透納氏症所引發的症狀就可能很輕微或甚至完全沒有出現<ref>{{cite web|title=What causes Turner syndrome?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/conditioninfo/pages/causes.aspx|publisher=Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development|accessdate=2015-03-15|date=2012-11-30|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402171740/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/conditioninfo/pages/causes.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。診斷方式基本就是根據臨床症狀以及[[基因檢測|基因檢測]]<ref>{{cite web|title=How do health care providers diagnose Turner syndrome?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/conditioninfo/Pages/diagnosed.aspx|publisher=Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development|accessdate=2015-03-15|date=2012-11-30|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402104716/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/conditioninfo/Pages/diagnosed.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 治療 ==
<!-- Treatment -->
目前沒有任何已知的醫療方式可以治療透納氏症，但卻多少對於緩和病徵有些幫助<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Tx/> -->。舉例來說，在幼童發育時期注射[[生長激素|生長激素]]可以在之後的成人階段增加身高<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Tx/> -->。{{tsl|en|Estrogen replacement therapy||雌激素替代療法}}能促進[[乳房|乳房]]以及[[臀部|臀部]]發育<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Tx/> -->。在確定有哪些健康問題是由於透納氏症造成後，才開始考慮需要怎樣的醫療照護來加以控制<ref name=NIH2012Tx>{{cite web|title=What are common treatments for Turner syndrome?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/conditioninfo/pages/treatment.aspx|publisher=Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development|accessdate=2015-03-15|date=2012-11-30|archive-date=2015-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150329003549/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/conditioninfo/Pages/treatment.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
<!-- History -->
產婦生出罹患透納氏症女童的機率大約介於1/2,000到1/5,000<ref name="ArchDisChild">{{cite journal | author = Donaldson MD, Gault EJ, Tan KW, Dunger DB | title = Optimising management in Turner syndrome: from infancy to adult transfer | journal = Arch. Dis. Child | volume = 91 | issue = 6 | pages = 513–520 | date = June 2006 | pmid = 16714725 | pmc = 2082783 | doi = 10.1136/adc.2003.035907 | url = http://adc.bmj.com/content/91/6/513.abstract | last2 = Gault | last3 = Tan | last4 = Dunger | access-date = 2016-06-28 | archive-date = 2012-03-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120307084228/http://adc.bmj.com/content/91/6/513.abstract | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Marino|first1=Bradley S.|title=Blueprints pediatrics|date=2013|publisher=Wolters Kluwer/Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|location=Philadelphia|isbn=9781451116045|page=319|edition=Sixth edition.|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OsmaeXtE7sQC&pg=PA319|access-date=2016-06-28|archive-date=2019-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323023914/https://books.google.com/books?id=OsmaeXtE7sQC&pg=PA319|dead-url=no}}</ref>。全球各地區與文化在透納氏症患者人數上基本相似，並沒有顯著的特異性<ref name=NIH2012Epi>{{cite web|title=How many people are affected or at risk?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/conditioninfo/pages/risk.aspx|publisher=Eunice Kennedy Shriver National Institute of Child Health and Human Development|accessdate=2015-03-15|date=2012-11-30|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402104713/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/turner/conditioninfo/pages/risk.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。透納氏症患者的平均壽命較一般人短，這是因為病患多有心臟方面的問題與糖尿病<ref name=NEJM2004>{{cite journal | author = Sybert VP, McCauley E | title = Turner's syndrome | journal = [[新英格兰医学杂志|N. Engl. J. Med.]] | volume = 351 | issue = 12 | pages = 1227–38 | date = September 2004 | pmid = 15371580 | doi = 10.1056/NEJMra030360 | last2 = McCauley }}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Henry Turner (endocrinologist)|亨利·透納 (內分泌學家)|亨利·透納}}是第一個在1938年描述此病症的醫生<!-- <ref name=Kel818/> -->，於1964年時，後人更進一步發現這是由於染色體異常所導致的疾病<ref name=Kel818>{{cite book|last1=Kelly|first1=Evelyn B.|title=Encyclopedia of human genetics and disease|date=2013|publisher=Greenwood|location=Santa Barbara, Calif.|isbn=9780313387142|page=818|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SjfKybobUIYC&pg=PA818|access-date=2016-06-28|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309053528/https://books.google.com/books?id=SjfKybobUIYC&pg=PA818|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

